/**
 * SVG elements are case-sensitive.
 *
 * @see {@link https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/SVG/Element#SVG_elements_A_to_Z}
 */
var CASE_SENSITIVE_TAG_NAMES = [
  'animateMotion',
  'animateTransform',
  'clipPath',
  'feBlend',
  'feColorMatrix',
  'feComponentTransfer',
  'feComposite',
  'feConvolveMatrix',
  'feDiffuseLighting',
  'feDisplacementMap',
  'feDropShadow',
  'feFlood',
  'feFuncA',
  'feFuncB',
  'feFuncG',
  'feFuncR',
  'feGaussainBlur',
  'feImage',
  'feMerge',
  'feMergeNode',
  'feMorphology',
  'feOffset',
  'fePointLight',
  'feSpecularLighting',
  'feSpotLight',
  'feTile',
  'feTurbulence',
  'foreignObject',
  'linearGradient',
  'radialGradient',
  'textPath'
];

module.exports = {
  CASE_SENSITIVE_TAG_NAMES: CASE_SENSITIVE_TAG_NAMES
};
